### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get single contact by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/69062a4e21df8e20b2609464

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "phone": "+55 11 939503930",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/69062a4e21df8e20b2609464
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "johnsmith@example.com",
  "phone": "+55 11 939503931",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/69062a4e21df8e20b2609464

